# Server Admin Popup Config - UI Specification

## Layout
Form container: max-width 800px, scrollable, with sticky save button at bottom.

## Component Breakdown

### Form Header
- Title: "Popup Configuration"
- Subtitle: "Customize what users see when they join your server"
- Save button: Primary color, disabled during save, shows spinner

### Basic Info Section
**Server Name Input**
- Label: "Server Name"
- Type: text input
- Max length: 100 characters
- Help text: "Displayed in popup header"

**Server Icon Input**
- Label: "Server Icon URL"
- Type: text input (URL)
- Validation: Valid image URL
- Preview: 64x64 thumbnail next to input
- Help text: "Square image recommended (256x256+)"

### Visual Section
**Server Banner Input**
- Label: "Banner Image URL"
- Type: text input (URL)
- Validation: Valid image URL
- Preview: 16:9 thumbnail (200px wide)
- Help text: "Wide image recommended (1920x1080)"

**Time Format Selector**
- Label: "Server Time Format"
- Type: dropdown select
- Options: "12-hour (AM/PM)" | "24-hour"
- Default: 24-hour

### Content Section
**MOTD Editor**
- Label: "Message of the Day"
- Type: textarea (4 rows)
- Max length: 500 characters
- Character counter
- Help text: "Basic markdown supported: **bold**, *italic*, [links]()"

**Welcome Message Editor**
- Label: "Welcome Message"
- Type: textarea (4 rows)
- Max length: 500 characters
- Character counter
- Help text: "Use {username} to insert user's name"
- Example preview below: "Welcome, DemonFiend!"

### Events Section
**Placeholder**
- Label: "Events" (with "Coming Soon" badge)
- Content: Gray box with "Future feature: announcements, polls, and scheduled events"
- Style: Subtle border, muted colors to indicate disabled state

## Form Behavior
- Auto-save draft to localStorage every 30 seconds
- Confirm dialog if user navigates away with unsaved changes
- Validation errors appear inline below each field
- Success toast on successful save
- Error toast with details on failed save

## Styling Notes
- Use consistent spacing (gap-4 between sections, gap-2 within sections)
- Input fields: full width with consistent height
- Previews: border, rounded corners, subtle shadow
- Disabled save button: reduced opacity + cursor-not-allowed
- Mobile: stack previews below inputs
